embeds.title: Roles
embeds.description: The most important roles a user can be granted in this server are described below.

fields.value: <@&1192955705066528910> - This small team only serves to manage this server, reviewers and their reviews, and bots. They have no influence over Ryder's decision in sending levels. Currently the team is <@164072941645070336>, and <@978613302483644486>. You can reach out to these people for questions or concerns about this server or a review.
<@&1192955803418775612> - Reviewers leave reviews on level requests that request feedback. This team is decided by Ryder alone and has no influence over Ryder's decision to send a level.
